data.description: Spacious home on the far east of El Paso, about 20 mins to Fort Bliss. Home has five bedrooms and two bathroom. Open floor plan living area, dining and kitchen. Master bathroom has two walk-in closets, double sink, two walk-in closet and large tub . Carpets in all bedrooms and tile in main area. Two car garage located in the rear of the home. Refrigerated A/C unit, covered back patio, with garage access at rear of home. Also includes refrigerator, gas stove, dishwasher and microwave.
